  ('dietitian-moex-07531', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-101-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關人體的超氧物歧化（superoxide dismutase, SOD）之敘述，何者正確？', '["在粒線體中的SOD結構之必要成分為鎂", "在血漿與細胞外液之SOD結構之必要成分為錳", "在細胞質之SOD結構之必要成分為銅與鋅", "在紅血球中之SOD結構之必要成分為鐵"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:47+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "86729168c010", "answer_pdf_sha1": "823fcb4b04db", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "101110", "c": "105", "s": "0302", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "營養學", "year": "101", "exam_name": "101年第2次醫事人員考試", "original_question_number": 27, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-07532', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-101-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '人體代謝鋅的過程中，金屬硫蛋白（metallothionein）的功能為何？', '["在小腸絨毛細胞內結合被吸收的鋅，避免過量的鋅進入血管內", "負責在血液循環中運送鋅", "在肝臟中鋅的主要儲存型態", "在骨骼與肌肉中鋅的主要儲存型態"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:47+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "86729168c010", "answer_pdf_sha1": "823fcb4b04db", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "101110", "c": "105", "s": "0302", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "營養學", "year": "101", "exam_name": "101年第2次醫事人員考試", "original_question_number": 28, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-07533', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-101-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關錳的代謝或功能之敘述，何者正確？', '["是超氧物歧化（superoxidase dismutase）的必要成分，在細胞質中發揮抗氧化功能", "是觸（catalase）的必要成分，在過氧化小體（peroxisomes）中發揮抗氧化功能", "身體藉著膽汁排除與小腸再吸收調節體內的錳含量", "由於腸道吸收率很低，因此沒有錳中毒的疑慮"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:47+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "86729168c010", "answer_pdf_sha1": "823fcb4b04db", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "101110", "c": "105", "s": "0302", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "營養學", "year": "101", "exam_name": "101年第2次醫事人員考試", "original_question_number": 29, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL)
